**(F) Requirement: DrivePowerInterface**

**(G) Requirement: TorqueGeneration**

22. Definition of requirement fullVehicleMassLimit as a VehicleMassLimitationRequirement.

24. fullVehicleMassLimit sets massReqd = 2000[kg].
25. fullVehicleMassLimit has an assumed constraint: vehicle.fuelMass == vehicle.fuelFullMass.

**(J) Part: Engine**
30. Definition of part Engine.

32. Engine performs action generateTorque of type GenerateTorque.

**(K) Requirement: vehicleSpecification**
33. Definition of requirement vehicleSpecification.
34. vehicleSpecification has subject vehicle of type Vehicle.
35. vehicleSpecification requires fullVehicleMassLimit.
36. vehicleSpecification requires emptyVehicleMassLimit.

**(L) Requirement: engineSpecification**
37. Definition of requirement engineSpecification.
38. engineSpecification has subject engine of type Engine.
39. engineSpecification has requirement drivePowerInterface of type DrivePowerInterface, subject = engine.clutchPort.
40. engineSpecification has requirement torqueGeneration of type TorqueGeneration, subject = engine.generateTorque.

**(M) Actions**
41. Definition of action 'provide power'.
42. Definition of action 'generate torque' as a subaction of 'provide power'.

**(N) Part: vehicle_c1**
43. Definition of part vehicle_c1 of type Vehicle.
44. vehicle_c1 performs 'provide power'.
45. vehicle_c1 has part engine_v1 of type Engine.
46. engine_v1 has port clutchPort.
47. engine_v1 performs 'provide power'.'generate torque' as generateTorque.

**(O) Part: 'Vehicle c1 Design Context'**
48. Definition of part 'Vehicle c1 Design Context'.

50. 'Vehicle c1 Design Context' satisfies vehicleSpecification by vehicle_design.
51. 'Vehicle c1 Design Context' satisfies engineSpecification by vehicle_design.engine_v1.
